    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Difficult asthma

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with potential allergic bronchopulmonary aspergillosis i.e. with peripheral
             blood eosinophilia, sputum eosinophilia, or any sputum production and bronchiectasis

          -  A history of smoking

          -  Significant occupational or environmental exposures

          -  Evidence on emphysema on chest high resolution computed tomography (HRCT) scan
      </textblock>
